creator: Conneqtech
descriptionHtml:
Our connected bike and smart app will give thieves a run for their money. Gone are the days your bike gets stolen, never to be found again.

Our app grants you a near real-time 24/7 insight in your bike's current location and whereabouts, even if it's not you riding the bike. The GPS is installed inside your bike and gives you peace of mind wherever your bike takes you.

Would you like to receive notifications when you enter or leave a location? Then this app has you covered, you can create as many virtual 'geofences' as your like that alert you and anyone that has access to your bike whenever your bike reaches those locations.

Excited about doing better for your health and the environment? We will show you how you are performing when you ride your bike, with daily, weekly, monthly and yearly statistics about travelled distance, burned calories, top speed and most importantly saved CO2 emissions. Leave your car in the garage and make yourself and our planet healthier!

Do you want to experience that special bike ride you took last week, but unsure what path you travelled? With our automatic ride generation, you can easily find that beautiful backroad and stunning vistas without taking a wrong turn.

In a nutshell:
- Live location of your bike
- Historic locations for the past year
- Virtual fences to protect against theft with push messaging
- Easy sharing with friends and family
- Automatic ride generation when you take your bike for a spin
descriptionShort: With the AXA IN App you will be able to track and trace your connected bike.

In a nutshell:
- Live location of your bike
- Historic locations for the past year
- Virtual fences to protect against theft with push messaging
- Easy sharing with friends and family
- Automatic ride generation when you take your bike for a spin

descriptionHtml:
Our connected bike and smart app will give thieves a run for their money. Gone are the days your bike gets stolen, never to be found again.

Our app grants you a near real-time 24/7 insight in your bike's current location and whereabouts, even if it's not you riding the bike. The GPS is installed inside your bike and gives you peace of mind wherever your bike takes you.

Would you like to receive notifications when you enter or leave a location? Then this app has you covered, you can create as many virtual 'geofences' as your like that alert you and anyone that has access to your bike whenever your bike reaches those locations.

Excited about doing better for your health and the environment? We will show you how you are performing when you ride your bike, with daily, weekly, monthly and yearly statistics about travelled distance, burned calories, top speed and most importantly saved CO2 emissions. Leave your car in the garage and make yourself and our planet healthier!

Do you want to experience that special bike ride you took last week, but unsure what path you travelled? With our automatic ride generation, you can easily find that beautiful backroad and stunning vistas without taking a wrong turn.

In a nutshell:
- Live location of your bike
- Historic locations for the past year
- Virtual fences to protect against theft with push messaging
- Easy sharing with friends and family
- Automatic ride generation when you take your bike for a spin
